North America (USA, Canada) & 189 (42\%) & 412 (37\%) \\
Europe (UK, Germany, France, etc.) & 156 (35\%) & 398 (36\%) \\
East Asia (Japan, China, S. Korea) & 67 (15\%) & 186 (17\%) \\
Other (Australia, S. America, Africa) & 36 (8\%) & 120 (11\%) \\
\midrule
University student samples & 312 (70\%) & --- \\
General population & 94 (21\%) & --- \\
Clinical populations & 42 (9\%) & --- \\
