\item \textbf{Meta-Analysis Results:} Pooled effect sizes, 95\% confidence intervals, prediction intervals, I\textsuperscript{2}, $\tau^2$ for all four core units
\item \textbf{Quality Assessments:} Risk of bias scores, GRADE evidence quality profiles
\item \textbf{Publication Bias:} Funnel plot data, Egger's test statistics, trim-and-fill estimates
\item \textbf{Brain Region Mappings:} 540 unique brain regions with unit associations
\item \textbf{R\textsuperscript{3} Coordinates:} 976 unique claims with R\textsuperscript{3} dimensions across 1,116 total claims analyzed
\end{itemize}

\textbf{Software Requirements:}
\begin{itemize}[leftmargin=*, topsep=2pt, itemsep=1pt]
\item Python 3.10+ (scipy, numpy, pandas, matplotlib for meta-analysis)
\item LaTeX distribution (for manuscript compilation)
\item LLM API access (for replication of extraction pipeline; models A, B, C, D not specified for reproducibility)
