\textbf{Reproducibility:} All analysis scripts include seed values and version information. Meta-analysis calculations can be reproduced using the provided JSON data files and Python scripts. The extraction pipeline (Stage 1) requires LLM API access; intermediate consensus outputs are available in the repository.

